snippet.title: FINAL Match Highlights - ARG 3:3 FRA (4:2 PEN) - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Lionel Messi starred for Argentina in his last #FIFAWorldCup match as La Albiceleste ended their 36-year wait for the elusive trophy.

In what can arguably be termed as one of the best finals of all-time, Argentina enjoyed a two-goal lead till the 80th minute courtesy of Lionel Messi converting a spot-kick in the 23rd minute and Angel Di Maria's brilliant strike in the 36th minute. 

However, a quick-fire brace from Kylian Mbappe brought the defending champions back in the game to take it to extra-time.

Messi scored his second of the night to restore Argentina's lead, but his Paris Saint-Germain teammate went on to complete his hat-trick to bring Didier Deschamps' side level again; and becoming the first player since 1966 to score a hat-trick in a World Cup Final.

In the penalty shootout, Lionel Messi along with Paula Dybala, Leandro Parades, and Gonzalo Montiel scored from the spot to secure the ultimate prize in #Qatar2022. While Mbappe & Randal Kolo Muani got scored, Kingsley Coman had his shot saved and Aurelien Tchouameni fired wide; thus handing the coveted trophy to the South American giants.

Enjoy the best moments from #ARGFRA and relive all the action from the #WorldsGreatestShow on #JioCinema & #Sports18 üì∫üì≤

snippet.title: Santa Hog Rider Saves Clashmas!
snippet.description:
Santa Hog Rider has arrived to the Village and Arena!
Play the Super Santa Hog Rider Challenge now in Clash Royale and Special Clashmas Challenges in Clash of Clans!

Merry Clashmas!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashRoyale/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashroyale

Enter the Arena! Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don‚Äôt want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device‚Äôs settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clas... or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-serv...

Parent‚Äôs Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Oppenheimer - Only In Theaters 7 21 23

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX¬Æ-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine ‚ÄúKitty‚Äù Oppenheimer. Oscar¬Æ winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award¬Æ nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar¬Æ nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment‚Äôs Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX¬Æ 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX¬Æ black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan‚Äôs films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

Siyani Episode 130 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 20th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran‚Äôs mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter‚Äôs nature and doesn‚Äôt stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran‚Äôs family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Directed By: Ali Akbar

snippet.description:
Episode 3646: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Inspector Chaalu Pandey reaches the Gokuldham society with his team and informs Bhide that they were unable to find Popatlal. Everyone prays for Popatlal and Bhide that they should live in peace and harmony but get scared by the entry of the police. Bhide informs the Gokuldham members that he had complained against Popatlal at the police station and Chalu Pandey is here to look for him. Watch the episode to know more.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3647 - Popatlal Ki Talaash?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Gruha Pravesam || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Gruha Pravesam MCM

In this new Middle Class Madhu episode, Madhu strikes up a humorous chat with the milkman and her father arrives bearing a grocery list for a special occasion. When Madhu arrives with the supplies from Budatha's store, he realises that the event is their new home's opening. Madhu urges Mahesh to make elaborate arrangements for the newly built house in her happiness. Mahesh, Balli, and Budatha set up everything in front of the new house, but they eventually realise that the property belongs to the manager and not the madhus. Have a lovely weekend and watch the new video Gruhapravesam's(HOUSE WARMING) humorous conclusion.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3645 - 19 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3645: 
--------------------------------------------------------
When Bhide gets to the police station, he complains about his friend Popatlal going missing. However, inspector Chaalu Pandey quarrels and complains, which irritates Bhide, who then files a report against Popatlal. Inspector Chaalu Pandey traps him with a condition that if he withdraws the complaint against Popatlal, the police will have the right to arrest him. Watch the episode to know more. 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3645, 19 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Siyani Episode 129 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 19th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran‚Äôs mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter‚Äôs nature and doesn‚Äôt stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran‚Äôs family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

snippet.title: WOH (Official Video) - Ikka x Dino James x Badshah | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‚ÄòWoh.‚Äô The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is one of the very few records which portray a man‚Äôs emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah‚Äôs verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‚ÄòWoh‚Äô is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

Stream Now on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/1QUU43rTDMnGl4xyaIfsYN
Record Label - Def Jam India / Universal Music
